            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="info">
                <div class="icon icon-rose">
                    <i class="material-icons">favorite</i>
                </div>
                <h4 class="info-title">Earn and Grow</h4>
                <p> Task owner can review your work and Rate your capabilities. The more Tasks you complete, the more credibility you earn. </p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

